<MudText Class="pa-5" Typo="Typo.h5">The Released Project</MudText>
<MudText Class="pa-10">
	My first 'released' game was for a promotional competition that Unity ran with Lego. They released the Ninjago assets in Unity 2020 showcasing node-like programming capabilities with the lego block based system. Building on Scratch in
	some respects. this enabled rapid protoyping with a familiar scene for kids (and adults!). The competition was to create an engaging one-buttom game, the winner of which would have thier game in Lego stores as well as a great haul of
	lego goodies! I didn't win in the end!
</MudText>
